  "body": "### Description\n\nCurrently, to run the application locally in prod mode you must package the application then locate the JAR and launch it via the java command.\r\nHowever, the location of the JAR is non standard and depends of which type of packaging is used.\r\n\r\nProviding a way to package and run the application in one command would be a great improvements to the developer experience.\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n```shell\r\n# Using quarkus CLI\r\nquarkus run\r\n\r\n# Using Maven\r\nmvn quarkus:run\r\n\r\n# Using Gradle\r\ngradle quarkusRun\r\n```\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
